OL,3,CEngland fans defy distances as
OL,4,Chundreds gather on eve of World Cup
OL,5,Copener
OL,7,FHundreds of England fans battled Texas-
OL,8,Fsized distances to gather in a packed
OL,9,Fpub on the eve of the Three Lions
OL,10,FWorld Cup opener.
OL,12,FSupporters created a sea of St
OL,13,FGeorge's flags, turned out in fancy
OL,14,Fdress and sang popular chants as they
OL,15,Fdescended on the Londoner pub on
OL,16,FMockingbird Lane in the hot Dallas
OL,17,Fsunshine on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781671667
OL,3,CEngland fans defy distances as
OL,4,Chundreds gather on eve of World Cup
OL,5,Copener
OL,7,FOrganiser John Gallivan, 39, told the
OL,8,FPress Association the scale of Texas
OL,9,Fhad made it far harder for fans to
OL,10,Ffind each other than at previous
OL,11,Ftournaments in Europe.
OL,13,FHe said well-known England fans Andy
OL,14,FMilne, Steve Bracknell and the Tango
OL,15,FMan would all be in attendance at the
OL,16,Fevent, saying the party atmosphere was
OL,17,F"what we come away for".
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
