CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781671667
OL,3,CEngland fans defy distances as
OL,4,Chundreds gather on eve of World Cup
OL,5,Copener
OL,7,FThe event comes the night before
OL,8,FEngland's first game at the AT&T
OL,9,FStadium in nearby Arlington against
OL,10,FCroatia.
OL,12,FHe said: "America's massive, it's so
OL,13,Fbig, so vast.
OL,15,F"When we go to Europe, it's really
OL,16,Feasy ` you know where you're going to
OL,17,Fbe.
OL,19,F"You don't have to ask, you don't have
OL,20,Fto look, you just know where we're
OL,21,Fgoing to be.
OL,26,@tD@JOUwD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
