SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781671667
OL,3,CEngland fans defy distances as
OL,4,Chundreds gather on eve of World Cup
OL,5,Copener
OL,7,F"In America, that's impossible ` so
OL,8,Fthe whole idea of today was to just
OL,9,Ffind somewhere, get them to put a deal
OL,10,Fon the beer and then advertise it."
OL,12,FThere was no police presence at the
OL,13,Fevent as supporters wearing England-
OL,14,Fthemed costumes and draped in St
OL,15,FGeorge's flags filled the pub
OL,16,Fthroughout the evening, with chants of
OL,17,F"It's Coming Home" and "Don't take me
OL,18,Fhome" breaking out as more fans
OL,19,Farrived.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@cO]yD@AOUyD@RO]yD@XOUzD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
