SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781671667
OL,3,CEngland fans defy distances as
OL,4,Chundreds gather on eve of World Cup
OL,5,Copener
OL,7,FMr Gallivan said the event had grown
OL,8,Ffar beyond his expectations after
OL,9,Fsharing it on social media.
OL,11,F"We've been here since 4pm and it's
OL,12,Fbeen grand. I feel sorry for the bar
OL,13,Fstaff," he said.
OL,15,F"I pushed it so hard, I think I was an
OL,16,Fevent planner in another life.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@GO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781671667
OL,3,CEngland fans defy distances as
OL,4,Chundreds gather on eve of World Cup
OL,5,Copener
OL,7,F"I put it on the supporters' travel
OL,8,Fclub Facebook page and it's just
OL,9,Fspiralled and spiralled and spiralled
OL,10,F` and we've got Andy Milne, Steve
OL,11,FBracknell, Tango Man ` they're all
OL,12,Fcoming here tonight. So it kind of
OL,13,Fsells itself.
OL,15,F"If you're an England fan and you want
OL,16,Fto sing and drink, come here."
OL,18,FThe event was ultimately shut down by
OL,19,Fpolice just before 10pm, with the
OL,20,Fvenue at maximum capacity and only two
OL,21,Fsecurity guards on duty.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOUxD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781671667
OL,3,CEngland fans defy distances as
OL,4,Chundreds gather on eve of World Cup
OL,5,Copener
OL,7,FDespite multiple police vehicles
OL,8,Farriving at the scene to ensure the
OL,9,Fbar was vacated, England fans remained
OL,10,Fin their numbers on the venue's
OL,11,Fbalcony.
OL,13,FEarlier, Mr Gallivan said many regular
OL,14,FEngland supporters had been unable to
OL,15,Fmake the trip because of the cost of
OL,16,Fattending the tournament.
OL,18,FHe said: "I think the way FIFA have
OL,19,Fmanaged it, it's been disgraceful.
OL,20,FWe've been dealt a bad hand.
OL,26,@zD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781671667
OL,3,CEngland fans defy distances as
OL,4,Chundreds gather on eve of World Cup
OL,5,Copener
OL,7,F"We could have brought so many more
OL,8,Fout here, but sadly they've been
OL,9,Foutpriced.
OL,11,F"People that I spent time with in
OL,12,FAlbania and Latvia and had a really
OL,13,Fgood night with, who go home and away,
OL,14,Fthey've been priced out of it and
OL,15,Fthat's not right. They shouldn't have
OL,16,Fbeen."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
