CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781671667
OL,3,CEngland fans defy distances as
OL,4,Chundreds gather on eve of World Cup
OL,5,Copener
OL,7,FHe said he was already looking ahead
OL,8,Fto England's next group game in
OL,9,FBoston, where he hoped to organise
OL,10,Fanother gathering for travelling
OL,11,Fsupporters.
OL,13,F"I've reached out to several outlets
OL,14,Fin Boston and I'm waiting to see who
OL,15,Fcan do the best deal," he said.
OL,17,F"Whoever can do the best deal, I'll
OL,18,Fget everyone to go there."
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@VO]yD@AOUzD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
