OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781671667
OL,3,CEngland fans defy distances as
OL,4,Chundreds gather on eve of World Cup
OL,5,Copener
OL,7,FMr Gallivan also said England
OL,8,Fsupporters had received a warm welcome
OL,9,Ffrom Texans since arriving in the
OL,10,FUnited States.
OL,12,FHe said: "Anywhere I go, whether it's
OL,13,Fbuying a drink in a shop or ordering
OL,14,Ffood, as soon as I order, they go, 'Oh
OL,15,Fwait, where are you from? Britain?
OL,16,FEngland?'. They're excited to have you
OL,17,Fhere.
OL,19,F"So that whole narrative that England
OL,20,Fare disliked is not true at all."
OL,26,@tD@JOU{D@AOU|D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781671667
OL,3,CEngland fans defy distances as
OL,4,Chundreds gather on eve of World Cup
OL,5,Copener
OL,7,FFor Mr Gallivan, the atmosphere
OL,8,Fcreated by fellow supporters before
OL,9,Fkick-off is as important as the
OL,10,Ffootball itself.
OL,12,F"That's literally what we come away
OL,13,Ffor," he said. "To be honest, this is
OL,14,Fmore to me than the actual match.
OL,16,F"The night before every England game
OL,17,Fis what we're here for ` the singing,
OL,18,Fthe dancing, the whole lot.
OL,20,F"There might even be karaoke later,
OL,21,Fwho knows?"
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@EO]uD@POUxD@AOU|D@AOU}D@KO]
